#. type: multicols*
#: sections/player_turns.tex:169
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\vspace*{-1em}\n"
"Every time you \\textbf{gain} Morale, discard a Negative Morale card (if you have any); otherwise:\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\setlength\\itemsep{0mm}\n"
"  \\item In \\pagelink{Adventure and Skirmish Modes}{Adventure and Skirmish}: Search(2) Positive Morale card and put the unwanted card to the bottom of the Deck.\n"
"  \\item In regular games: draw 1 Positive Morale card.\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"You may have \\textbf{2 Positive Morale cards at a time}.\n"
"Don't draw a third card.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\vspace*{-1em}\n"
"每当你\\textbf{获得}士气时，弃置一张低落士气牌（如果有）；否则：\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\setlength\\itemsep{0mm}\n"
"  \\item 在\\pagelink{Adventure and Skirmish Modes}{冒险和遭遇战}中：搜寻（2）张高昂士气牌，并将不要的牌放到牌堆底部。\n"
"  \\item 在常规游戏中：抽1张高昂士气牌。\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"你同一时间可以拥有\\textbf{2张高昂士气牌}。%\n"
"不要抽第三张牌。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/player_turns.tex:173
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\smallskip\n"
"Every time you \\textbf{lose} Morale, discard a Positive Morale card (if you have any); otherwise draw 1 Negative Morale card (no Searching!).\n"
"You may have an \\textbf{unlimited number of Negative Morale cards}.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\smallskip\n"
"每当你\\textbf{失去}士气时，弃置一张高昂士气牌（如果你有）；否则抽取1张低落士气牌（不能搜寻！）。%\n"
"你可以拥有\\textbf{不限数量的低落士气牌}。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/player_turns.tex:181
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\smallskip\n"
"Place newly gained Morale cards face up near your Hero Board.\n"
"Positive Morale cards may be used at any moment you wish.\n"
"Negative Morale cards must be used the next time when the situation indicated by the card occurs.\n"
"\\textbf{Put used cards at the bottom of their respective Decks}.\n"
"If you must draw a Morale card but the respective Morale Deck is empty, reshuffle its Discard Pile to form a new Deck.\n"
"\\end{expansion}"
msgstr ""
"\\smallskip\n"
"将新获得的士气牌正面朝上放在你的英雄面板旁。%\n"
"高昂士气牌可在你希望的任何时刻使用。%\n"
"低落士气牌必须在下次发生牌上所示情况时使用。%\n"
"\\textbf{将使用过的牌放到各自牌堆的底部}。%\n"
"如果你必须抽一张士气牌，但对应的士气牌堆为空，则将其弃牌堆重新洗混，形成新的牌堆。\n"
"\\end{expansion}"
